title: Przewóz, Opole Voivodeship
summary:
Przewóz [ˈpʂɛvus] (German: Przewos, 1934–45: Fährendorf) is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Cisek, within Kędzierzyn-Koźle County, Opole Voivodeship, in south-western Poland. It lies approximately 8 kilometres (5 mi) south-east of Cisek, 15 km (9 mi) south of Kędzierzyn-Koźle, and 54 km (34 mi) south-east of the regional capital Opole.
The village has a population of 345.
